=========================[ ORDERING VIA COMPUSERVE ]==========================

Only Episode 1, INTO THE STORM, is available as Shareware. Register now and
you will receive two more episodes, WHIRLPOOL OF DEATH and HEART OF THE FIRE,
each with different background graphics and enemy craft, giving a massive 75
levels of high-speed arcade action.

The registration fee for AstroFire is $29.95 (US Dollars).
This includes all packing and postage costs to anywhere in the world.
The game will ONLY be supplied on a 720K 3.5" disk.

If you have a modem and a CompuServe account, the fastest and easiest way to
register AstroFire is on-line through the GO SWREG service. Just follow the
on-screen instructions (the Registration ID for AstroFire is 2558).

Once you have registered AstroFire, the registration fee will be charged to
your CompuServe account. CompuServe will inform me of your name and address
and I will ship your order as soon as possible, but please allow up to 28
days for delivery.

If you have any questions about the on-line registration procedure, send a
message to the Shareware Administrator by selecting the "Provide Feedback"
option at the main SWREG menu.

If you have any questions about your order, or if you require product details
or technical support, send a message to myself, Owen Thomas. My CompuServe ID
number is 100334,412.

